    <section class="guide-takeaways">
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>3 years of business tax returns and monthly P&amp;Ls are non-negotiable for any buyer or SBA lender</li>
        <li>The SDE recast and add-back schedule must have a documentation reference for every line item — undocumented add-backs don't survive diligence</li>
        <li>Bank statements reconciled to P&amp;Ls are the fastest way to establish financial credibility with skeptical buyers</li>
        <li>A well-organized virtual data room signals professional management and accelerates diligence</li>
        <li>Start organizing documents now — not the week you list</li>
      </ul>
